{"tid":1524513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今晚831黑警亂打人，我地唔可以再忍","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:26:15.000Z","uid":170347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a8c1f2183491b50906841087482d35fa56f353","tid":1524513,"uid":170347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"一次又一次咁打被捕者<br />\n我地就被射眼，放催淚彈當飯食<br />\n即使我地幾嬲，第二日既記招講既藉口有幾廢<br />\n我地都仲係咩都做唔到呀<br />\n佢地一啲應有既懲罰都冇呀 輸既一直只有我地<br />\n我地對唔對得住我地被捕被打既手足呀！？<br />\n佢地次次都變本加厲，已經樽頸位啦大家！<br />\n<br />\n無辜市民跪底求饒都要照比你顏射胡椒！<br />\n15歲炸！15歲無啦啦比你打到爆肛！<br />\n警察已經唔再係保護而係殘害緊香港市民呀！<br />\n<br />\n現在宣布：不能再容忍黑警，無個無辜！<br />\n開學一定要話比啲狗仔狗女親身體驗佢地父母做既好事！切勿手軟！<br />\n仲有睇下可唔可以拉一兩隻狗入人群報復！<br />\n<br />\n同埋，一定要推上國際法庭，<br />\n強烈要求**解散香港現有警隊**"},{"pid":"abb220eb0e806312b272f617a23f170f64994c53","tid":1524513,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:25:40.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70m7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=6e19af93\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70m7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=0719fa3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70m7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=f01917fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4c